OL,3,CMan charged with murder in Abergavenny
OL,5,FA man has been charged with murder
OL,6,Ffollowing the death of a man in
OL,7,FAbergavenny.
OL,9,FLiam Bennett, 27, of Oak Tree Lane,
OL,10,FGilwern, has been remanded into
OL,11,Fcustody to appear before Newport
OL,12,FMagistrates' Court on Saturday 23 May.
OL,14,FOfficers from Gwent Police were called
OL,15,Fto Old Hereford Road, Abergavenny at
OL,16,Faround 6:15am on Friday 15 May after a
OL,17,Fman was left with life-threatening
OL,18,Finjuries.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
