OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1779700298
OL,3,CMan charged with murder in Abergavenny
OL,5,FA man in his 20s was taken to
OL,6,Fhospital, where he died. His family
OL,7,Fare being supported by specialist
OL,8,Fofficers.
OL,10,FSenior investigating officer,
OL,11,FDetective Chief Inspector Ellen
OL,12,FJoslyn, said: "Our thoughts remain
OL,13,Fwith the victim's family and friends
OL,14,Fat this difficult time.
OL,16,F"We would like to thank the community
OL,17,Ffor their support whilst we
OL,18,Finvestigate the circumstances of this
OL,19,Ftragic death.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
