OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1779700298
OL,3,CMan charged with murder in Abergavenny
OL,5,F"We understand that reports of this
OL,6,Fnature can be concerning to our
OL,7,Fcommunities.
OL,9,F"While our enquiries continue over the
OL,10,Fcoming days, you are likely to see an
OL,11,Fincreased number of officers in the
OL,12,Farea."
OL,14,FGwent Police is asking anyone who was
OL,15,Fin the area at the time, or who saw
OL,16,Fanything suspicious, to get in touch,
OL,17,Fparticularly those who may have
OL,18,Fdashcam, CCTV, or doorbell footage
OL,19,Ffrom Old Hereford Road or Underhill
OL,20,FCrescent and the surrounding area
OL,21,Faround the time of the incident.
